score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8cd7a2a18ffbb8f2c4941574d98bc3b771c9a8fc","tid":1569071,"uid":117462,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"你幾時有錯過覺得我地贏過？由出世果刻做香港人已經是輸家啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"好多和理非都唔係人生輸家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"分化分得咁低莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dab63c21f403294cb26d715faab9ea9ecfe53b","tid":1569071,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb9623598261c6dde2292527ac723586b3ea50b","tid":1569071,"uid":143210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:32:22.000Z","msg":"起底都唔駛都記得你條三毛"},{"pid":"b474846c49aff5157b988d3f34c6d005c74d24c3","tid":1569071,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"其實好同意"},{"pid":"e7dd9afa7dd93ce3dea575d785db41a2e0ed2bdf","tid":1569071,"uid":3318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695653ed521bbedf74ae1c87a379c7a82dc89a3c","tid":1569071,"uid":276625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"宜家仲有屌左膠同分化<br />\n仲話打fa 係咩事呀"},{"pid":"3ec2cdb38d2acd764c122d4077f38a082b6e7d19","tid":1569071,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"[決戰藍絲攻略]相對論, 和理非=藍絲, 勇武=速龍<br />\n<br />\n和理非同藍絲一樣, 二百萬大把任拉<br />\n勇武同黑警一樣, 係寶貴資源<br />\n<br />\n對家出藍絲, 我地出和理非<br />\n衝突爆發, 對家出黑警, 我地出勇武<br />\n勇武同作為突擊隊, 同速龍一樣, 有事才出動, 完事即撤<br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n-勇武進場同離場要快過黑警(~15min), 衝突前事先plan好路線<br />\n-勇武不需去衝突前線, 可以突襲對家後方, 方便離場(而且後方通常冇記者, 去哂衝突前線)<br />\n-阻膠同藍絲一樣, 大把唔駛錫住, 將佢地當三角路障推埋藍絲到"},{"pid":"7e59b3d39a38fe04726c8797fa0fa481b40cd58e","tid":1569071,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1567102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1567102/page/1</a><br />\n[黨鐵封站]避免走難式遊行, 參考番8.5罷工遍地開花<br />\n而家次次走難式遊行示威, 遲早趕走d和理非, 越搞越少人<br />\n<br />\n建議參考番8.5罷工遍地開花, 可以先係商場聚人, 之後出去快閃堵路<br />\n<br />\n另外可嘗試100萬人坐爆港鐵, telegram約定同一時間出站遊行一小時<br />\n落車後在站內儲人, 儲滿後就出發, 目標做成各區堵路<br />\n<br />\n一小時後再入番去坐爆港鐵, 無限loop"},{"pid":"ad5d9bc832ef6e24363e7c9e3c55e5cf52851cbf","tid":1569071,"uid":42402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"聽日見啦屌"},{"pid":"d7b30a0c07ac63ceae7cd4d41ddd5861d79b5c4d","tid":1569071,"uid":266747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"食屎啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da74ff1b1cab50153ae138c38592ca44e1ff4e8","tid":1569071,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"起底 block 不推文"},{"pid":"54125aed6ca6491d09f71c373fa46d7a5f4415f6","tid":1569071,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"一日開9個post咁多 咁努力帶風向 有冇錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db97d086e9fb95d02e347d34de0bb78e04bee24e","tid":1569071,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da74ff1b1cab50153ae138c38592ca44e1ff4e8","tid":1569071,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"起底 block 不推文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"唔好block 要follow <br />\n佢一開post我地就入黎屌9佢 咁樣佢先唔會帶到風向"},{"pid":"7106994a9c37b955e36eee54bc1f39ccd4b3ad97","tid":1569071,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9f18a746721ce128b53bce50384ace2d0f471e","tid":1569071,"uid":1